{"tid":945811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：不擔心美國會隨意變動《香港政策法》，因有利於美國企業在港活動","createTime":"2018-12-18T07:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:39:04.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"00c177a3299378304cdf7851bf8e99864622ecbf","tid":945811,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"在中美貿易戰陰霾下，全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳今早接受港台訪問時稱，中央絕對會避免將香港捲入中美間的紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥第二次上京述職，昨日分別獲國家主席習近平和國務院總理李克強接見。李克強在開場發言中，特別提到「在國際形勢錯綜複雜的情形下，香港作為自由港和單獨關稅區，經濟保持了平穩增長，來之不易」。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳認為李克強說法，並不是回應早前美國國會轄下「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」年度報告中針對香港的言論，而是反映中央有決心繼續保留香港自由港和獨立關稅區的特色。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳更指，不擔心華府會隨意變動《香港政策法》，因《香港政策法》有利於美國企業在港活動，預料若華府更改《香港政策法》，中美關係會進一步緊張，中央將會向美國報復。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，中央絕對會避免將香港捲入中美間紛爭，因中央希望在「一國兩制」下，讓香港擔當中西方之間的橋樑，即使未來中美或中西方交惡，雙方仍可藉香港有所往來。"},{"pid":"489e79006aeef79f45cba0b227fb7884ae0421ff","tid":945811,"uid":13663,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"中國（1年前）：不擔心美國會隨意發動貿易戰，因中國市場有利於美國企業及農業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f2d738f975da8298eab6f30e26c98655b9a834","tid":945811,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44219a13dec289e65d97106fc600963e1fb4152","tid":945811,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"In short<br />\n劉兆佳：因為美國拿起石頭扔自己腳會痛, 怕痛所以唔會變"},{"pid":"4bd5def6ed05ac70e7b6a05433aefcc315b86c59","tid":945811,"uid":222445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44219a13dec289e65d97106fc600963e1fb4152","tid":945811,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"In short<br />\n劉兆佳：因為美國拿起石頭扔自己腳會痛, 怕痛所以唔會變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"咩理論"},{"pid":"4f56322e73d341d8847e454d65dcbe729c98b532","tid":945811,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bd5def6ed05ac70e7b6a05433aefcc315b86c59","tid":945811,"uid":222445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44219a13dec289e65d97106fc600963e1fb4152","tid":945811,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"In short<br />\n劉兆佳：因為美國拿起石頭扔自己腳會痛, 怕痛所以唔會變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"咩理論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"中國理論"},{"pid":"0ef09c275af9408ffd58f044a77d16d7db2dec0c","tid":945811,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過又一隻靠讀鬼佬書上位屌返鬼佬搵食既共狗咁囉！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/18/163018_760429d1e8098a95f372057a5062993c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F163018_760429d1e8098a95f372057a5062993c.png&h=a2a9e4b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49fe5b7db16276d27a3ab909969a9b2c1fedee74","tid":945811,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"人地取消完出張美企白名單咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efb5d2f648fd6eb4077c6c5380f8c85a1752f37","tid":945811,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489e79006aeef79f45cba0b227fb7884ae0421ff","tid":945811,"uid":13663,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"中國（1年前）：不擔心美國會隨意發動貿易戰，因中國市場有利於美國企業及農業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3b2b9e2c860a7455a5ffc17c09bcdb073a17b2","tid":945811,"uid":68620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n依家講緊支那利用緊香港做一d唔得光事情<br />\n相信浸浸在限期內有機會取消，唔比支那有空隙"},{"pid":"ad2c9a05d968353d2964f2d0ba8784b3f06da84b","tid":945811,"uid":10101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"麥當勞都賣左比中資"},{"pid":"65482e862714ef346fcf91542ed3af74469a1b34","tid":945811,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥當勞都賣左比中資</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實情係支那蝈企，又要靠買人港澳Franchise扮鬼佬乞錢乍！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923cd026077e0d709e07ff03c4bb87d76c2100ca","tid":945811,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳依d叫分析? 響環球時報抄咪有囉!"},{"pid":"fa012002d9a1b9d40e88df11683d53c13bd01dfa","tid":945811,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"○三年預言「三萬人」遊行遭非議<br />\n【本報訊】原是中文大學社會學講座教授的劉兆佳，在○二年港府實施問責制後加盟中央政策組，自此由經常在傳媒鞭撻港府施政失誤的學者，搖身一變成為專替港府為民情把脈的「民意天線」，<strong>但○三年七一遊行前夕，他低估遊行人數，指估計僅約三萬人參加，最終五十萬人上街，震撼了整個特區政府，劉兆佳被譏「天線失效」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110304/00176_002.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110304%2F00176_002.html&d=7SyFeUAMhhGDowNAKCjD98mB%2BETt